did.unittitle: Divinity School, Yale University, photographs and memorabilia

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The materials consist of photographs of faculty, students, and various school related events. Included is an index of students in 1942 and a group portrait of the Yale Divinity School Class of 1889.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 21 (YRG 21), Records of the Yale Divinity School.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Divinity School, Yale University, Photographs and Memorabilia (RU 772). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged by accession.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of photographs of faculty, students, and various school related events. Included is an index of students in 1942 and a group portrait of the Yale Divinity School Class of 1889.
